{{! Sheet Header }}
<header class='sheet-header'>

  <div class="header-top flexrow">
  
    <div class="left-col flexcol">
      <h1>Class Name</h1>
      <input
        class='document-name'
        name='name'
        type='text'
        value='{{actor.name}}'
        placeholder='Name'
      />
    </div>
  
    <div class="right-col flexrow">
      <div class="flexcol">
        <h3>Class Dice: D6</h3>
        <p>
          You can add your D6 to your dice pool any time you’re acting in a foolish, daring or cavalier fashion. In any dice pool which includes the Fool’s D6, you gain:
        </p>
        <p>
          <b>Special:</b> Roll another D6 and add it to the present dice pool.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="systems/die-rpg/assets/icons/d6-exploded.svg" width="100"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="header-bottom flexrow">
    <div class="left-col flexcol">
      <img
        class='profile-img'
        src='{{actor.img}}'
        data-edit='img'
        data-action='onEditImage'
        title='{{actor.name}}'
        height='100'
        width='100'
      />

      <div class="class-description">
        <p>
          You read a sad story. You cry. Do you think that’s sinister, as if someone has artificially taken over your emotions? Of course not. That’s just what art is.
        </p>
        <p>
          Anyone who’s ever met a Dictator would disagree.
        </p>
        <p>
          By performing, they alter other people’s emotional states. Dictators play people like a musician plays a harp. They can pluck the strings. They can snap them.
        </p>
        <p>
          They’re like bards, if everyone was fucking petrified of bards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='header-fields right-col'>
      <h2>Stats</h2>
      <div class='stats flexrow'>
        {{#each system.stats as |stat key|}}
          <div class='stat flexcol flex-group-center'>
            <label
              class='resource-label rollable flexlarge align-left'
              data-action='statRoll'
              data-stat-name="{{key}}"
              data-label='{{localize (lookup @root.config.stats key)}}'
            >{{localize (lookup @root.config.statAbbreviations key)}}</label>
            <input
              type='text'
              name='system.stats.{{key}}.value'
              value='{{stat.value}}'
              class="stat-score"
              data-dtype='Number'
            />
          </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{! The grid classes are defined in scss/global/_grid.scss. To use,
        use both the "grid" and "grid-Ncol" class where "N" can be any number
        from 1 to 12 and will create that number of columns.  }}
      <div class='resources grid grid-4col'>

        {{! "flex-group-center" is also defined in the _grid.scss file
          and it will add a small amount of padding, a border, and will
          center all of its child elements content and text. }}

        {{!-- Health --}}
        <div class='resource flex-group-center'>
          <label for='system.health.value' class='resource-label'>
            {{localize 'DIE_RPG.Resource.hea.long'}}
          </label>
          <div class='resource-content flexrow flex-center flex-between'>
            <input
              type='text'
              name='system.resources.health.value'
              value='{{system.resources.health.value}}'
              data-dtype='Number'
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        {{!-- Guard --}}
        <div class='resource flex-group-center'>
          <label for='system.resources.guard.value' class='resource-label'>
            {{localize 'DIE_RPG.Resource.gua.long'}}
          </label>
          <div class='resource-content flexrow flex-center flex-between'>
            <input
              type='text'
              name='system.resources.guard.value'
              value='{{system.resources.guard.value}}'
              data-dtype='Number'
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        {{!-- Willpower --}}
        <div class='resource flex-group-center'>
          <label for='system.resources.willpower.value' class='resource-label'>
            {{localize 'DIE_RPG.Resource.wil.long'}}
          </label>
          <div class='resource-content flexrow flex-center flex-between'>
            <input
              type='text'
              name='system.resources.willpower.value'
              value='{{system.resources.willpower.value}}'
              data-dtype='Number'
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        {{!-- Defense --}}
        <div class='resource flex-group-center'>
          <label for='system.resources.defense.value' class='resource-label'>
            {{localize 'DIE_RPG.Resource.def.long'}}
          </label>
          <div class='resource-content flexrow flex-center flex-between'>
            <input
              type='text'
              name='system.resources.defense.value'
              value='{{system.resources.defense.value}}'
              data-dtype='Number'
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  

  
  
</header>